item.title: CVE-2022-4049|2024-08-03T01:27:54.126Z -- unknown -- wp%20user
item.description: The WP User WordPress plugin through 7.0 does not properly sanitize and escape a parameter before using it in a SQL statement, leading to a SQL injection exploitable by unauthenticated users.
